He noted that his committee in particular and the State government in general is willing to partner with the London based club to develop football in Akwa Ibom State.

The Sports Committee Chairman maintained that his vision is to ensure that football in the State is taken to the next level even as he disclosed he has began contacting FC Porto of which when final arrangement is concluded, an academy of the Portuguese based club would be established in Akwa Ibom State.


			
